msg: Because most callers of svn_fs_x__get_dag_node don't need to hold on to
the returned node, they will be just as happy with a temporary object.
Add a function that gives them just that.
svn_fs_x__make_path_mutable): We need those nodes only tempoarily,
thus call the the new function.
add_descendant_mergeinfo): Request only temporary DAG nodes where
we won't need them to survive a second
